    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Concessio in <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">emphyteusim</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrarum</rs> in loco vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions"
                            >Alberi</placeName>, facta a <persName><name ref="Pertualdus"
                                >Bretaldo</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Pulcella"
                                >Pulcella</name></persName> iugalibus et aliis consortibus, favore
                                <persName><name ref="Alfredus">Alfredi</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Petrus de Blata">Petri de
                            Blata</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Berta"
                            >Berthę</name></persName> uxoris eius et heredum. Actum in <rs
                            key="#Vici">vico</rs>
                        <placeName>S. Laurentii qui vocatur in Funi</placeName>, rog. <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>, 1063, 19 martii, Henrici imperatoris VIII,
                        indictione I.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, vol. 2, doc. 38 (in preparazione).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
